        "html": "<section id=\"shopify-section-template--24940377080074__before_after_image_qQ78FT\" class=\"shopify-section shopify-section--before-after-image\" style=\"--clip-path-offset: -145.6px;\"><style>\n  #shopify-section-template--24940377080074__before_after_image_qQ78FT {\n    --section-background-hash: 0;\n  }\n\n  #shopify-section-template--24940377080074__before_after_image_qQ78FT + * {\n    --previous-section-background-hash: 0;\n  }</style>\n<style>\n  #shopify-section-template--24940377080074__before_after_image_qQ78FT {\n    --section-stack-intro: 33.3333%;\n    --section-stack-main: 66.6667%;\n\n    --before-after-initial-drag-position: 63%;\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"section   section-blends section-full\">\n  <div class=\"section-stack section-stack--horizontal \">\n<div class=\"section-stack__intro\">\n        <div class=\"prose \">\n          <p class=\"subheading\">TESTÉ CLINIQUEMENT</p>\n<h2 class=\"h2\">Nous ne promettons pas des résultats. Nous les prouvons.</h2>\n<p>Des études cliniques indépendantes, ainsi que des milliers de clientes satisfaites, confirment l’efficacité de notre <strong>Masque au Bio-Collagène</strong>.<br><br>Dès les premières applications, la peau paraît <strong>plus ferme, plus lisse et plus éclatante</strong>, avec une <strong>réduction visible des ridules, des taches pigmentaires et des cernes</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Voyez la différence dès la 1ère utilisation.</strong></p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n<div class=\"section-stack__main\">\n      <div class=\"before-after shadow  text-custom\" style=\"--text-color: 255 255 255;\">\n        <div class=\"before-after__before-image  text-custom\" style=\"--text-color: 255 255 255;\">\n<picture><img src=\"//leaf-cosmetics.com/cdn/shop/files/Untitled_design_35_430x_1.webp?v=1758389676&amp;width=430\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"//leaf-cosmetics.com/cdn/shop/files/Untitled_design_35_430x_1.webp?v=1758389676&amp;width=300 300w, //leaf-cosmetics.com/cdn/shop/files/Untitled_desi