8A.75.75 0 0 1 8 .25z\"></path>\n                    </svg>\n                  \n                </div>\n                <strong class=\"review-title\">Fini les imperfections</strong>\n              </div>\n\n              <!-- Badge vérifié (image) -->\n              \n                <div class=\"review-verified\">\n                  <img class=\"review-verified-badge\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0828/6457/0634/files/badge-facebook.png?v=1739294501\" alt=\"Verified badge\">\n                  <span>Client vérifié</span>\n                </div>\n              \n\n              <!-- Texte -->\n              <div class=\"review-text\">\n                \"J’ai une peau à tendance acnéique et j’avais peur que ce masque soit trop riche, mais au contraire ! Mes boutons ont diminué, mes pores sont resserrés et ma peau est beaucoup plus nette. C’est mon secret pour une peau sans défauts.\"\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      \n        <div class=\"reviews-slide\">\n          <!-- Carte -->\n          <div class=\"review-card\">\n            <!-- Images avant/après -->\n            <div class=\"review-card__images\">\n              <div class=\"review-card__image-left\">\n                <img src=\"//leaf-cosmetics.com/cdn/shop/files/11.png?crop=center&amp;height=500&amp;v=1740149697&amp;width=400\" alt=\"Before\" class=\"\" data-media-download-modified=\"true\" data-original-position=\"static\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n                \n                  <div class=\"review-badge-left\">AVANT</div>\n                \n              </div>\n              <div class=\"review-card__image-right\">\n                <img src=\"//leaf-cosmetics.com/cdn/shop/files/12.png?crop=center&amp;height=500&amp;v=1740149697&amp;width=400\" alt=\"After\" class=\"\" data-media-download-modified=\"true\" data-original-position=\"static\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n                \n                  <div class=\"review-badg