        "remove_vertical_spacing": true,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": true,
        "html": "<style>\n  .lyora-transform {\n    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;\n    background: #fff5ef;\n    padding: 28px 0 22px;\n    width: 100%;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n  }\n\n  .lyora-transform-header {\n    padding: 0 16px;\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-bottom: 18px;\n  }\n\n  .lyora-transform-title {\n    font-size: 22px;\n    font-weight: 800;\n    color: #111;\n    line-height: 1.25;\n    margin: 0 0 8px;\n  }\n\n  .lyora-transform-title em {\n    font-style: italic;\n    text-decoration: underline;\n    text-decoration-thickness: 2px;\n    text-underline-offset: 4px;\n  }\n\n  .lyora-transform-subtitle {\n    font-size: 13px;\n    color: #444;\n    line-height: 1.5;\n    margin: 0;\n    font-style: italic;\n  }\n\n  .lyora-timeline {\n    position: relative;\n    padding: 4px 16px 0 46px;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n  }\n\n  .lyora-line {\n    position: absolute;\n    left: 26px;\n    top: 6px;\n    bottom: 10px;\n    width: 2px;\n    background: #111;\n    border-radius: 2px;\n  }\n\n  .lyora-step {\n    position: relative;\n    padding: 14px 0 10px;\n  }\n\n  .lyora-pill {\n    display: inline-block;\n    background: #f7c948;\n    color: #111;\n    font-weight: 900;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    letter-spacing: .3px;\n    padding: 8px 12px;\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    border: 2px solid #111;\n    box-shadow: 0 2px 0 #111;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n  }\n\n  .lyora-step-title {\n    margin: 0 0 6px;\n    font-size: 18px;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n    font-weight: 800;\n    color: #111;\n  }\n\n  .lyora-step-text {\n    margin: 0;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    line-height: 1.65;\n    color: #1a1a1a;\n  }\n\n  .lyora-cta-wrap {\n    padding: 0 16px;\n    margin-top: 16px;\n  }\n\n  .lyora-cta {\n    display: block;\n    width: 100%;\n    text-align: center;\n    background: #f7c948;\n    color: #111;\n    font-weight: 900;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    padding: 16px 14px;\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    border: 3px solid #111;\n    box-shadow: 0 3px 0 #111;\n    text-decoration: none;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n  }\n\n  .lyora-cta:active {\n    transform: translateY(1px);\n    box-shadow: 0 2px 0 #111;\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 480px) {\n    .lyora-transform-title { font-size: 21px; }\n    .lyora-step-title { font-size: 17px; }\n    .lyora-pill { font-size: 12px; padding: 7px 10px; }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"lyora-transform\">\n\n  <div class=\"lyora-transform-header\">\n    <h2 class=\"lyora-transform-title\">\n      Ihre <em>Transformation</em> Woche<br>für Woche\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"lyora-transform-subtitle\">Von der ersten Kapsel zu nachhaltigen Ergebnissen</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"lyora-timeline\">\n    <div class=\"lyora-line\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div>\n\n    <div class=\"lyora-step\">\n      <div class=\"lyora-pill\">TAGE 1-3</div>\n      <h3 class=\"lyora-step-title\">Der Sanfte Start</h3>\n      <p class=\"lyora-step-text\">\n        Ihr Körper nimmt die aktiven Inhaltsstoffe auf und die Entgiftung beginnt. Eine leichte Müdigkeit in den ersten Tagen?\n        Das ist normal — Ihr Körper eliminiert endlich.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"lyora-step\">\n      <div class=\"lyora-pill\">WOCHE 1-2</div>\n      <h3 class=\"lyora-step-title\">Die Detox Aktiviert Sich</h3>\n      <p class=\"lyora-step-text\">\n        Leber befreit, Parasiten gezielt bekämpft. Regelmäßigere Verdauung und erste Energieschübe.\n        Ihr Körper verlässt den \"Überlebensmodus\".\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"lyora-step\">\n      <div class=\"lyora-pill\">WOCHEN 3-4</div>\n      <h3 class=\"lyora-step-title\">Die Ersten Echten Veränderungen</h3>\n      <p class=\"lyora-step-text\">\n        Blähungen reduziert, leichtes Aufwachen, stabile Energie den ganzen Tag. Flacherer Bauch, strahlende Haut.\n        Es wird sichtbar.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"lyora-step\">\n      <div class=\"lyora-pill\">1 MONAT UND +</div>\n      <h3 class=\"lyora-step-title\">Die Dauerhafte Transformation</h3>\n      <p class=\"lyora-step-text\">\n        Tiefe Widerstandsfähigkeit etabliert. Optimale Leber, ausgeglichener Darm, nachhaltige Energie.\n        Die Ergebnisse bleiben — sie verschwinden nicht.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"lyora-cta-wrap\">\n    <a class=\"lyora-cta\" href=\"#\">Jetzt Starten</a>\n  </div>\n\n</div>",
