        "html": "<style>\n  .lyora-comparison-section {\n    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;\n    padding: 40px 20px;\n    background: #fff5ef; /* ✅ fond demandé */\n    max-width: 100%;\n  }\n\n  .lyora-comparison-container {\n    max-width: 600px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 32px;\n  }\n\n  .lyora-comparison-header {\n    text-align: center;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n\n  .lyora-comparison-title {\n    font-size: 24px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #1a1200;\n    line-height: 1.3;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n  }\n\n  .lyora-comparison-title u {\n    text-decoration: underline;\n    font-style: italic;\n  }\n\n  .lyora-comparison-subtitle {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-style: italic;\n    color: #444;\n    line-height: 1.5;\n    max-width: 450px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  /* Image centrale */\n  .lyora-comparison-image {\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 500px;\n    height: auto;\n    display: block;\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    background: #fff5ef; /* ✅ fond demandé derrière l'image si transparence/chargement */\n  }\n\n  /* CTA Button */\n  .lyora-comparison-cta {\n    display: block;\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 380px;\n    padding: 18px 24px;\n    background: #f7c948;\n    color: #1a1200;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    font-weight: 800;\n    text-align: center;\n    letter-spacing: 0.5px;\n    border: 3px solid #1a1200;\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);\n    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;\n    text-decoration: none;\n  }\n\n  .lyora-comparison-cta:hover {\n    transform: translateY(-2px);\n    box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);\n  }\n\n  /* Responsive */\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .lyora-comparison-section {\n      padding: 32px 16px;\n    }\n\n    .lyora-comparison-title {\n      font-size: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .lyora-comparison-subtitle {\n      font-size: 13px;\n    }\n\n    .lyora-comparison-image {\n      max-width: 100%;\n    }\n\n    .lyora-comparison-cta {\n      font-size: 14px;\n      padding: 16px 20px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"lyora-comparison-section\">\n  <div class=\"lyora-comparison-container\">\n    \n    <!-- Header -->\n    <div class=\"lyora-comparison-header\">\n      <h2 class=\"lyora-comparison-title\">Warum LYORA Die Konkurrenz <u>Schlägt</u>\n</h2>\n      <p class=\"lyora-comparison-subtitle\">\n        Medikamente aus der Apotheke behandeln nur ein Symptom mit Nebenwirkungen. LYORA behandelt Leber, Parasiten und Darm in einer natürlichen Lösung.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Image (remplace tout le tableau) -->\n    <!-- 👇 REMPLACE CETTE URL PAR L'URL DE TON IMAGE UPLOADÉE DANS SHOPIFY 👇 -->\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0990/1765/4619/files/hf_20260228_204253_68ae659e-8f7d-4aec-94e7-51b262212f88.jpg?v=1772312863\" alt=\"LYORA vs Medikamente Vergleich\" class=\"lyora-comparison-image\">\n\n    <!-- CTA Button -->\n    <button class=\"lyora-comparison-cta\">Ich Treffe Die Richtige Wahl</button>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- \n📝 INSTRUCTIONS :\n1. Va dans Shopify Admin > Contenu > Fichiers\n2. Upload ton image de comparaison LYORA\n3. Copie l'URL de l'image\n4. Remplace l'URL de l'image ci-dessus par ton URL\n-->",
