     <span class=\"lyora-review-verified\">\n                <svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"#4CAF50\"><path d=\"M13.854 3.646a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-7 7a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0l-3.5-3.5a.5.5 0 1 1 .708-.708L6.5 10.293l6.646-6.647a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0z\"></path></svg>\n                Verifizierter Käufer\n              </span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"lyora-review-rating-row\">\n              <div class=\"lyora-review-stars\">\n                <svg viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"#FFD300\"><path d=\"M3.612 15.443c-.386.198-.824-.149-.746-.592l.83-4.73L.173 6.765c-.329-.314-.158-.888.283-.95l4.898-.696L7.538.792c.197-.39.73-.39.927 0l2.184 4.327 4.898.696c.441.062.612.636.282.95l-3.522 3.356.83 4.73c.078.443-.36.79-.746.592L8 13.187l-4.389 2.256z\"></path></svg>\n                <svg viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"#FFD300\"><path d=\"M3.612 15.443c-.386.198-.824-.149-.746-.592l.83-4.73L.173 6.765c-.329-.314-.158-.888.283-.95l4.898-.696L7.538.792c.197-.39.73-.39.927 0l2.184 4.327 4.898.696c.441.062.612.636.282.95l-3.522 3.356.83 4.73c.078.443-.36.79-.746.592L8 13.187l-4.389 2.256z\"></path></svg>\n                <svg viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"#FFD300\"><path d=\"M3.612 15.443c-.386.198-.824-.149-.746-.592l.83-4.73L.173 6.765c-.329-.314-.158-.888.283-.95l4.898-.696L7.538.792c.197-.39.73-.39.927 0l2.184 4.327 4.898.696c.441.062.612.636.282.95l-3.522 3.356.83 4.73c.078.443-.36.79-.746.592L8 13.187l-4.389 2.256z\"></path></svg>\n                <svg viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"#FFD300\"><path d=\"M3.612 15.443c-.386.198-.824-.149-.746-.592l.83-4.73L.173 6.765c-.329-.314-.158-.888.283-.95l4.898-.696L7.538.792c.197-.39.73-.39.927 0l2.184 4.327 4.898.696c.441.062.612.636.282.95l-3.522 3.356.83 4.73c.078.443-.36.79-.746.592L8 13.187l-4.389 2.256z\"></path></svg>\n                <svg viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"#FFD300\"><path d=\"M3.612 15.443c-.386.198-.824-.149-.746-.592l.83-4.73L.173 6.765c-.329-.314-.158-.888.283-.95l4.898-.696L7.538.792c.197-.39.73-.39.927 0l2.184 4.327 4.898.696c.441.062.612.636.282.95l-3.522 3.356.83 4.73c.078.443-.36.79-.746.592L8 13.187l-4.389 2.256z\"></path></svg>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"lyora-review-date\">vor 2 Wochen</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"lyora-review-body\">\n          Ich habe schon viele Detox-Produkte ausprobiert, aber LYORA ist das Beste! Keine unangenehmen Nebenwirkungen, natürliche Inhaltsstoffe und ich sehe bereits nach 3 Wochen Ergebnisse. Mein Energielevel ist viel höher!\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"lyora-review-badge\">Bewertung per Shop-Einladung</span>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Review 4 -->\n      <div class=\"lyora-review-item\">\n        <div class=\"lyora-review-header\">\n          <div class=\"lyora-review-avatar\">JW</div>\n          <div class=\"lyora-review-meta\">\n            <div class=\"lyora-review-author\">\n              Julia W.\n              <span class=\"lyora-review-verified\">\n                <svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"#4CAF50\"><path d=\"M13.854 3.646a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-7 7a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0l-3.5-3.5a.5.5 0 1 1 .708-.708L6.5 10.293l6.646-6.647a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0z\"></path></svg>\n                Verifizierter Käufer\n              </span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"lyora-review-rating-row\">\n              <div class=\"lyora-review-stars\">\n                <svg viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"#FFD300\"><path d=\"M3.612 15.443c-.386.198-.824-.149-.746-.592l.83-4.73L.173 6.765c-.329-.314-.158-.888.283-.95l4.898-.696L7.538.792c.197-.39.73-.39.927 0l2.184 4.327 4.898.696c.441.062.612.636.282.95l-3.522 3.356.83 4.73c.078.443-.36.79-.746.592L8 13.187l-4.389 2.256z\"></path></svg>\n                <svg viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"#FFD300\"><path d=\"M3.612 15.443c-.386.198-.824-.149-.746-.592l.83-4.73L.173 6.765c-.329-.314-.158-.888.283-.95l4.898-.696L7.538.792c.197-.39.73-.39.927 0l2.184 4.327 4.898.696c.441.062.612.636.282.95l-3.522 3.356.83 4.73c.078.443-.36.79-.746.592L8 13.187l-4.389 2.256z\"></path></svg>\n                <svg viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"#FFD300\"><path d=\"M3.612 15.443c-.386.198-.824-.149-.746-.592l.83-4.73L.173 6.765c-.329-.314-.158-.888.283-.95l4.898-.696L7.538.792c.197-.39.73-.39.927 0l2.184 4.327 4.898.696c.441.062.612.636.282.95l-3.522 3.356.83 4.73c.078.443-.36.79-.746.592L8 13.187l-4.389 2.256z\"></path></svg>\n                <svg viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"#FFD300\"><path d=\"M3.612 15.443c-.386.198-.824-.149-.746-.592l.83-4.73L.173 6.765c-.329-.314-.158-.888.283-.95l4.898-.696L7.538.792c.197-.39.73-.39.927 0l2.184 4.327 4.898.696c.441.062.612.636.282.95l-3.522 3.356.83 4.73c.078.443-.36.79-.746.592L8 13.187l-4.389 2.256z\"></path></svg>\n                <svg viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"#FFD300\"><path d=\"M3.612 15.443c-.386.198-.824-.149-.746-.592l.83-4.73L.173 6.765c-.329-.314-.158-.888.283-.95l4.898-.696L7.538.792c.197-.39.73-.39.927 0l2.184 4.327 4.898.696c.441.062.612.636.282.95l-3.522 3.356.83 4.73c.078.443-.36.79-.746.592L8 13.187l-4.389 2.256z\"></path></svg>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"lyora-review-date\">vor 1 Monat</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"lyora-review-body\">\n          Hervorragendes Produkt! Meine Verdauung hat sich deutlich verbessert und ich fühle mich insgesamt viel besser. Die Qualität der Inhaltsstoffe ist spürbar. Würde es jederzeit wieder kaufen!\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"lyora-review-badge\">Bewertung per Shop-Einladung</span>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Review 5 -->\n      <div class=\"lyora-review-item\">\n        <div class=\"lyora-review-header\">\n          <div class=\"lyora-review-avatar\">LM</div>\n          <div class=\"lyora-review-meta\">\n            <div class=\"lyora-review-author\">\n              Lars M.\n              <span class=\"lyora-review-verified\">\n                <svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"#4CAF50\"><path d=\"M13.854 3.646a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-7 7a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0l-3.5-3.5a.5.5 0 1 1 .708-.708L6.5 10.293l6.646-6.647a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0z\"></path></svg>\n                Verifizierter Käufer\n              </span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"lyora-review-rating-row\">\n              <div class=\"lyora-review-stars\">\n                <svg viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"#FFD300\"><path d=\"M3.612 15.443c-.386.198-.824-.149-.746-.592l.83-4.73L.173 6.765c-.329-.314-.158-.888.283-.95l4.898-.696L7.538.792c.197-.39.73-.39.927 0l2.184 4.327 4.898.696c.441.062.612.636.282.95l-3.522 3.356.83 4.73c.078.443-.36.79-.746.592L8 13.187l-4.389 2.256z\"></path></svg>\n                <svg viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"#FFD300\"><path d=\"M3.612 15.443c-.386.198-.824-.149-.746-.592l.83-4.73L.173 6.765c-.329-.314-.158-.888.283-.95l4.898-.696L7.538.792c.197-.39.73-.39.927 0l2.184 4.327 4.898.696c.441.062.612.636.282.95l-3.522 3.356.83 4.73c.078.443-.36.79-.746.592L8 13.187l-4.389 2.256z\"></path></svg>\n                <svg viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"#FFD300\"><path d=\"M3.612 15.443c-.386.198-.824-.149-.746-.592l.83-4.73L.173 6.765c-.329-.314-.158-.888.283-.95l4.898-.696L7.538.792c.197-.39.73-.39.927 0l2.184 4.327 4.898.696c.441.062.612.636.282.95l-3.522 3.356.83 4.73c.078.443-.36.79-.746.592L8 13.187l-4.389 2.256z\"></path></svg>\n                <svg viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"#FFD300\"><path d=\"M3.612 15.443c-.386.198-.824-.149-.746-.592l.83-4.73L.173 6.765c-.329-.314-.158-.888.283-.95l4.898-.696L7.538.792c.197-.39.73-.39.927 0l2.184 4.327 4.898.696c.441.062.612.636.282.95l-3.522 3.356.83 4.73c.078.443-.36.79-.746.592L8 13.187l-4.389 2.256z\"></path></svg>\n                <svg viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"#FFD300\"><path d=\"M3.612 15.443c-.386.198-.824-.149-.746-.592l.83-4.73L.173 6.765c-.329-.314-.158-.888.283-.95l4.898-.696L7.538.792c.197-.39.73-.39.927 0l2.184 4.327 4.898.696c.441.062.612.636.282.95l-3.522 3.356.83 4.73c.078.443-.36.79-.746.592L8 13.187l-4.389 2.256z\"></path></svg>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"lyora-review-date\">vor 1 Monat</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"lyora-review-body\">\n          Sehr zufrieden mit LYORA! Die Wirkung ist sanft aber effektiv. Ich hatte keinerlei Beschwerden während der Einnahme und bemerke eine deutliche Verbesserung meines Wohlbefindens. Top Preis-Leistung!\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"lyora-review-badge\">Bewertung per Shop-Einladung</span>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Pagination -->\n    <div class=\"lyora-pagination\">\n      <button class=\"lyora-page-btn active\">1</button>\n      <button class=\"lyora-page-btn\">2</button>\n      <button class=\"lyora-page-btn\">3</button>\n      <button class=\"lyora-page-btn\">...</button>\n      <button class=\"lyora-page-btn\">260</button>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>",
